  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个流程图，展示患者从社区到住院的完整路径，重点是出院阶段的access block mechanism。核心问题是：患者明明ready for discharge了，却因为外部原因滞留在医院。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Community",
        "Inpatient",
        "Ready",
        "access block mechanism"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。所以起点是Community，然后患者可能通过两条路径进入急诊？一条是直接ED arrival，另一条是先经过GP？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Community",
        "GP",
        "ED_Arrival"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，GP / primary care是常规路径，但很多人也会直接去急诊。这两条线在ED_Arrival汇合。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "GP",
        "ED_Arrival"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我把Community放在最左边，分出两条箭头：一条标注GP / primary care，另一条直接到ED arrival。GP那条也连到ED arrival。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Community",
        "GP",
        "ED_Arrival"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "接下来是ED assessment & treatment，然后有一个决策点Decision to admit，再进入Inpatient stay。这些是关键状态节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ED_Treat",
        "Admission",
        "Inpatient"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "ED_Treat、Admission、Inpatient——这三个都是状态节点对吧？我想用统一的视觉风格来区分它们。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ED_Treat",
        "Admission",
        "Inpatient"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "Admission是决策点，相对中性；但ED_Treat和Inpatient是真正的临床状态，需要突出。Ready for discharge也是个中性节点，之后才是问题所在。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ED_Treat",
        "Inpatient",
        "Ready",
        "Admission"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "明白了，我把ED_Treat和Inpatient用红色系填充，Admission和Ready用灰色中性色。现在到Ready for discharge之后，您说的blockages是什么？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ED_Treat",
        "Inpatient",
        "Ready",
        "state",
        "neutral"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "两个主要constraints：Aged care placement，这是容量约束，床位不够；还有NDIS supports / accommodation，审批慢或者不匹配。这两个都是risk节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Block_Aged",
        "Block_NDIS",
        "constraints",
        "risk"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "所以Block_Aged和Block_NDIS都是从Ready分出来的两条分支？它们会阻止患者真正离开医院？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Ready",
        "Block_Aged",
        "Block_NDIS"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，这两个blockages导致患者滞留在Inpatient，形成occupancy feedback loop——这是access block mechanism的核心。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Block_Aged",
        "Block_NDIS",
        "Inpatient",
        "occupancy feedback loop"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "我加上这两个risk节点，用橙色虚线边框表示警告。现在关键来了：这个feedback loop怎么画？是从Block_Aged连回Inpatient？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Block_Aged",
        "Inpatient",
        "risk",
        "dasharray"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "是的，虚线连接，标注\"occupancy feedback loop\"。另外还有一个效果：高占用率会限制ED的flow，所以Inpatient也要虚线连回ED_Treat。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Block_Aged",
