      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "两条虚线：一条是Block_Aged到Inpatient的反馈循环，另一条是Inpatient到ED_Treat的拥堵传导。这样整个access block机制就闭环了。",
      "elements_involved": [
