      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 15,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "等等，Block_NDIS也应该有类似的反馈效应吧？虽然主要是Aged care占床位多，但NDIS delay同样会造成滞留。",
